title: The Revolutionaries - Musical Dub Attack (Well Charge )
description:
Track Listing:
 Side 1:
 1. Semi Classical Natty Dread
 2. Musical Dub Attack
 3. Dub Sound
 4. Is Dub I A Deal With
 5. Dub Development
 6. Jamboree Dub

 Side 2:
 7. Sky Juice & Festival Dub
 8. Dub For Your Life
 9. Dub For Michael Holding
 10. Everybody Dubbin'
 11. Dub For Marcus Garvey





Top notch late seventies Channel One dub album originally issued in a plain sleeve in minute quantities.  It is in fact the dubwise companion to I Roy's 1978 album Musical Shark Attack, quite literally the mixes over which Roy chatted.  This re-issue, direct from master tape and replete with a great new sleeve, is courtesy of New York's DKR crew at last allows all of us to at last enjoy this rarity. 





Enjoyyy and Seed !!!
